Package: drawfield
Type: Package
Title: Plots various sport courts and fields
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Braden Sharp
Maintainer: Braden Sharp <braden.sharp.13@gmail.com>
Description: The `drawfield` package can be used to plot courts and fields
    of various sports. These plots serve as a base layer for other 
    visualizations, such as heat maps or shot diagrams.
